| Component      | Before (s08)     | After (s09)                |
|----------------|------------------|----------------------------|
| Tools          | 6                | 9 (+spawn/send/readInbox) |
| Agents         | Single           | Lead + N teammates         |
| Persistence    | None             | config.json + JSONL inboxes|
| Threads        | Background cmds  | Full agent loops per thread|
